Package com.filestack.errors

Custom exceptions for Filestack operations.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FilestackException
    Base Exception subclass for all checked library exceptions.
    FilestackRuntimeException
    Base RuntimeException subclass for all unchecked library exceptions.
    InternalException
    Thrown when an unexpected error occurs in the library or Filestack service.
    InvalidArgumentException
    Thrown to indicate a method was passed invalid arguments.
    InvalidParameterException
    Thrown to indicate a request had invalid or missing parameters.
    PolicySignatureException
    Thrown to indicate a request had an issue with its policy or signature.
    ResourceNotFoundException
    Thrown when a resource (file handle, API Key, URL, etc) was not found.
    ValidationException
    Thrown to indicate invalid object state or method argument.
